    "body": "I can also confirm this behavior. I had the same problem running `hardhat node` with v2.9.2,  node transaction logs were not appearing even though the transactions themselves were successful.\r\n\r\nfor instance, deploying a new contract will not print the `eth_sendRawTransaction` log or changing automine with ` network.provider.send(\"evm_setAutomine\", [false])` will not print `evm_setAutomine` to the console.\r\n\r\nReverting to 2.9.1 solved the issue.\r\n\r\nHere is how I tested it:\r\n1) On a new VM I installed node/npm, then I created a new hardhat project and installed hardhat v2.9.2 globally with `sudo npm install hardhat@2.9.2 -g`\r\n2) I ran `hardhat node` and tried changing the mining behavior and deploying a dummy contract - no logs were printed.\r\n3) Did the same steps above but with `sudo npm install hardhat@2.9.1 -g` - logs appeared.",
